  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Meadow Assault, the ultimate multiplayer CO-OP adventure game where teamwork and strategy are key. Join forces with up to three other friends in a dynamic world teeming with possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/cf8745f4fbe5895bddacb86dd596339d.poster.avif?t=1729960431\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/cf8745f4fbe5895bddacb86dd596339d.webm?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/cf8745f4fbe5895bddacb86dd596339d.mp4?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer Mayhem</strong>: Team up with friends in online CO-OP mode for an immersive gaming experience.<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Cast</strong>: Choose from 11 unique characters (+ other customization), each with their own save.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/e01bcc035af24a501abcc0dbde6f45f6.poster.avif?t=1729960431\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/e01bcc035af24a501abcc0dbde6f45f6.webm?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/e01bcc035af24a501abcc0dbde6f45f6.mp4?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Keep Your Crops Thriving </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cultivate Variety</strong>: Plant a diverse range of crops and vegetables, each with unique needs and rewards.<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Harvest for Profit</strong>: Sell your bountiful harvest to upgrade your equipment and expand your farm.<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defend Your Yield</strong>: Protect your crops from marauding intruders and ensure a prosperous harvest.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/2dea13229fbd610e96665e5861b13c76.poster.avif?t=1729960431\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/2dea13229fbd610e96665e5861b13c76.webm?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/2dea13229fbd610e96665e5861b13c76.mp4?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Gather resources </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Riches</strong>: Explore procedurally generated landscapes<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize Your World</strong>: Shape the environment to suit your needs and preferences, turning the wilderness into your personal paradise.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/7bee71c6c71e52054d22710dce8b93a8.poster.avif?t=1729960431\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/7bee71c6c71e52054d22710dce8b93a8.webm?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/7bee71c6c71e52054d22710dce8b93a8.mp4?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Keep the wildlife under control </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nature's Challenges: Confront and overcome the dangers posed by the untamed wilderness.<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master Your Domain: Establish dominance over the local wildlife to maintain balance and safety in your domain.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Meadow Assault, the ultimate multiplayer CO-OP adventure game where teamwork and strategy are key. Join forces with up to three other friends in a dynamic world teeming with possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/cf8745f4fbe5895bddacb86dd596339d.poster.avif?t=1729960431\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/cf8745f4fbe5895bddacb86dd596339d.webm?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/cf8745f4fbe5895bddacb86dd596339d.mp4?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer Mayhem</strong>: Team up with friends in online CO-OP mode for an immersive gaming experience.<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Cast</strong>: Choose from 11 unique characters (+ other customization), each with their own save.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/e01bcc035af24a501abcc0dbde6f45f6.poster.avif?t=1729960431\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/e01bcc035af24a501abcc0dbde6f45f6.webm?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/e01bcc035af24a501abcc0dbde6f45f6.mp4?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Keep Your Crops Thriving </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cultivate Variety</strong>: Plant a diverse range of crops and vegetables, each with unique needs and rewards.<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Harvest for Profit</strong>: Sell your bountiful harvest to upgrade your equipment and expand your farm.<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defend Your Yield</strong>: Protect your crops from marauding intruders and ensure a prosperous harvest.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/2dea13229fbd610e96665e5861b13c76.poster.avif?t=1729960431\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/2dea13229fbd610e96665e5861b13c76.webm?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/2dea13229fbd610e96665e5861b13c76.mp4?t=1729960431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Gather resources </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Riches</strong>: Explore procedurally generated landscapes<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize Your World</strong>: Shape the environment to suit your needs and preferences, turning the wilderness into your personal paradise.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/7bee71c6c71e52054d22710dce8b93a8.poster.avif?t=1729960431\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939850/extras/7bee71c6c71e52054d